Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.27,0:01:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,许多光怪陆离  奇妙万千的现象\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And many of the weird and wondrous things
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.90,0:01:54.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就发生在我们身处的这个宇宙里\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}are happening right here in our own cosmic backyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.45,0:01:59.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太阳系真的是一个奇妙的地方\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Our Solar System is a really fantastic place.
