Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.85,0:07:45.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但肯定的是\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but there has to be
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.11,0:07:47.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土卫二冰层下应存在\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}a significant reservoir of liquid water
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.36,0:07:49.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个重要的"地下水库"\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}beneath the surface of Enceladus.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.58,0:07:54.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果土卫二地表下真的存在液态水\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}If liquid water exists beneath the surface,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.72,0:07:57.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中可能蕴含着大量有机分子\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It could be teeming with organic molecules.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.98,0:08:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有机分子以及适宜温度\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}These, along with relatively warm temperatures,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.80,0:08:04.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是创造生命的重要因素\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}are the essential ingredients for creating life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.80,0:08:07.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能在土卫二地表下\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It would be incredible
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.22,0:08:09.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现原始生命\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}if we were to find life, primitive life,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.64,0:08:11.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那将太不可思议了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}underneath the surface of Enceladus.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.43,0:08:15.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们并不指望出现类人生物\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We don't expect complex creatures such as ourselves
