Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.44,0:08:22.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此类能够在地球上独立存活的生命\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}independent of life on Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.63,0:08:25.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是有史以来最伟大的发现了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}would be one of the greatest discoveries ever.
