Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.81,0:08:55.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它是宇宙中最绚丽的景象之一\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}are among the most dazzling sights in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.75,0:09:00.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅行者号飞船对土星的第一次探测\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The Voyager spacecraft first visited Saturn
