Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.71,0:09:04.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在看到卡西尼号飞船提供的新影像\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and now with the new images provided by Cassini.
