Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.15,0:09:06.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像用3D眼镜看的一样真切\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's like putting on a pair of 3D glasses
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.26,0:09:08.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们首次细致详尽的看清\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}for the first time to be able to see with great detail
