Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.59,0:09:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也困扰了科学家们近几个世纪\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}has eluded scientists for centuries.
