Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.79,0:39:47.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生命起源于原始水洼中\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that life began in a primordial soup,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.23,0:39:51.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温暖的水汽中含有大量能源和大气成分\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}a warm pond containing energy and atmospheric elements
