Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.29,0:40:39.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论生命是怎样形成的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Regardless of how life started,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.08,0:40:41.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一次巧合\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}a fortunate event
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.36,0:40:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使得生命向复杂进化成为可能\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}made it possible for complex creatures to evolve.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.46,0:40:48.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大约30亿年前\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}About 3 billion years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.85,0:40:50.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原始的地下水细菌为了生存\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}ancient underwater bacteria
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.91,0:40:55.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始利用水  二氧化碳  太阳能\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}began to use water, Carbon Dioxide and the sun's energy
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.47,0:40:58.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化合生成碳水化合物\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to produce Carbohydrates in order to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.50,0:41:02.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个过程  被称作光合作用\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}This process, called Photosynthesis,
